95
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:41,839
gauge your classes. As the semester goes

96
00:02:39,519 --> 00:02:43,679
on, be mindful of what's in the syllabus

97
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:45,440
and what your professor generally uses

