126
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:31,599
New York 10 times, look at all the

127
00:03:30,158 --> 00:03:33,198
paintings each time you go through, and

128
00:03:31,598 --> 00:03:34,638
still know next to nothing about any of

129
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:36,478
the art there. You might know the

130
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:38,558
general layout where certain pieces are,

131
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:40,559
but if I ask you for details, which

132
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:43,040
artist created this painting, where was

133
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:45,199
this dog thing sculpted? You won't have

134
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:46,719
