135
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:48,719
Passively running your eyes over the

136
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:50,399
pages is like casually strolling through

137
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:52,238
an art museum and not actually studying

138
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:53,920
any of the pieces. It's actually worse

139
00:03:52,239 --> 00:03:55,598
